{"itemid":578,"subject":"FEVRE DREAM steaming your way","event":"The first issue of the FEVRE DREAM miniseries from Avatar Comics will be in the stores on Wednesday, I'm pleased to announce.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/0009w2r4/\"><img src=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/0009w2r4/s320x240\" width=\"155\" height=\"240\" border='0'/></a>\r\n\r\nThe series will run to ten issues.  The script/ adaptation was done by Daniel Abraham, author of the Long Price Quartet and creator of Jonathan Hive in the Wild Cards book.  Artwork by Rafa Lopez of Malaga, Spain.  \r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/0009x1p3/\"><img src=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/0009x1p3/s320x240\" width=\"155\" height=\"240\" border='0'/></a>\r\n\r\nThe original story, of course, is from my 1982 historical horror novel, FEVRE DREAM.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/0002gr2d/\"><img src=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/0002gr2d\" width=\"103\" height=\"150\" border='0'/></a>\r\n\r\nCheck it out.\r\n\r\nAnd if you'll be in the Chicago area this weekend, be sure to drop by the Chicago Comics & Entertainment Expo ( http://www.chicagocomicandentertainmentexpo.com/ )and get a signed copy at the Avatar booth, where I'll be hanging for most of the weekend.","ditemid":148116,"eventtime":"2010-04-13 16:50:00","props":{"taglist":"comic books","current_moodid":59,"commentalter":1288287783,"personifi_word_count":123,"opt_screening":"F","interface":"web","revnum":1,"personifi_tags":"8:5,10:11,11:11,42:5,36:11,1:5,29:5,3:35,5:5,25:8,4:23,26:2,9:29,nterms:yes","revtime":1271182681},"can_comment":0,"logtime":"2010-04-12 22:50:41","anum":148,"url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/148116.html","event_timestamp":1271177400,"reply_count":9,"comments":[{"collapsed":0,"shown":1,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/51443191/3030116","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/148116.html?replyto=9683604","name":"reply","tit